install Node.Js in your machine to run the program
install Postman for checking and testing of the api
open CMD promt 
type node -v (to check the version and if your machine has node.js)
Navigate to folder
type Code . (to open Visual Code)
Start By typing - npm init
type npm install express body-parser (to inject some dependencies)
if you dont have nodemon install (npm install -g nodemon)
run the code by typing - npm start
